Titolo: Geometry Wars: Retro Evolved

Anno: 2003

Descrizione: Geometry Wars is a video game made by Bizarre Creations. Initially a minigame in  Project Gotham Racing 2, an updated version, titled Retro Evolved, was eventually released for the Xbox 360. That version, at one point, held the record for the most downloaded Xbox Live Arcade Game.Retro Evolved was later included in the 2007 game Geometry Wars: Galaxies, the first game in the series to be released for non-Microsoft platforms.

Genere: Multidirectional shooter

Valutazione: 84
